# 🇨🇳 Cxcoinbankofchina

**Cxcoinbankofchina** is a modern, responsive online banking platform inspired by the Bank of China. Built with a clean red-and-white UI, it offers secure login, multilingual support, a dashboard, and transaction management — all deployable via Vercel and powered by NeonDB.

---

## 🌐 Live Demo

🔗 [Visit the app](https://xinbankofchina.vercel.app)

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🔐 **Secure Authentication**
  - Register/Login with validation
  - Email login supported
- 💼 **User Dashboard**
  - View balances, account summaries
- 💸 **Transactions**
  - Send, receive, and log transactions
- 🌍 **Translation Support**
  - i18n-ready (English / Chinese)
- 🎨 **Themed UI**
  - Red and white color scheme
- ☁️ **Vercel-Ready Deployment**
- 🧩 **Backend:**
  - Node.js + Express
  - Prisma ORM + NeonDB

